jeus.uddi.v3.api.request.inquiry

Class FindRelatedBusinesses

  • java.lang.Object
    • jeus.uddi.v3.AbstractRegistryObject
      • jeus.uddi.v3.api.request.inquiry.FindRelatedBusinesses
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, RegistryObject

    public class FindRelatedBusinesses
extends AbstractRegistryObject
    find_relatedBusinesses의 data type class. Used to locate information about businessEntity registrations that are related to a specific business entity whose key is passed in the inquiry.

    다음 schema는 UDDI version 3.0 Schema에서 인용한다. 

     <element name="find_relatedBusinesses" type="{urn:uddi-org:api_v3}find_relatedBusinesses"/>
 <complexType name="find_relatedBusinesses">
   <complexContent>
     <restriction base="{http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema}anyType">
       <sequence>
         <element ref="{urn:uddi-org:api_v3}authInfo" minOccurs="0"/>
         <element ref="{urn:uddi-org:api_v3}findQualifiers" minOccurs="0"/>
         <choice>
           <element ref="{urn:uddi-org:api_v3}businessKey"/>
           <element ref="{urn:uddi-org:api_v3}fromKey"/>
           <element ref="{urn:uddi-org:api_v3}toKey"/>
         </choice>
         <element ref="{urn:uddi-org:api_v3}keyedReference" minOccurs="0"/>
       </sequence>
       <attribute name="maxRows" type="{http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema}int" />
       <attribute name="listHead" type="{http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema}int" />
     </restriction>
   </complexContent>
 </complexType>
